ha [Hausa]: Muna bukatar musan gurin da zamu tura kudinku. Aje a saita

en [English]: A notification has been sent to your MPESA number **{{mobile}}**. Please check your phone to confirm.

ha [Hausa]: An aika sanarwar zuwa lambar MPESA ɗinka **{{mobile}}**. Da fatan za a duba wayarka don tabbatarwa.

ha [Hausa]: Sayi yanzu biya daga gaba ** {{amount}} ** zuwa ** {{customer}} **

en [English]: MPESA doesn't allow for decimal payments
ha [Hausa]: MPESA baya bada izinin biyan kuɗin goma
Farashin da ake dashi na drawndown

ha [Hausa]: Sako: kudin gaba daya za a karasu a balans din walet dinku\

ha [Hausa]: Adadin kudin da za a biya (yahada da {{amount}} Ladan cinikayya)
